@startuml diagrama de actividades WAIS

title WAIS

|User|
start
:Opens WAIS test card;

:Selects an option\nRegister / Modify / Consult;

if (Option selected?) then (Register or Modify)

  :Enters scores and notes;

  |System|
  :Shows live interpretation per field;

  |User|
  if (Wants to save?) then (yes)
    |System|
    :Saves results;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Exits;
    stop
  endif

else (Consult)

  |System|
  :Fetches and displays existing results;

  |User|
  :Exits;
  stop

endif

@enduml